trans-unit.source: Constructs an access condition such that an operation will be performed only if the resource's ETag value does not match the specified ETag value.
trans-unit.target: Constructs an access condition such that an operation will be performed only if the resource's ETag value does not match the specified ETag value.

trans-unit.source: The ETag value to check against the resource's ETag, or <codeInline>"*"</codeInline> to require that the resource does not exist.

trans-unit.target: An <codeEntityReference>T:Microsoft.WindowsAzure.Storage.AccessCondition</codeEntityReference> object that represents the If-None-Match condition.
